OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1780067467
OL,3,CTributes to 'loving father' allegedly
OL,4,Ckilled in street
OL,6,FIn a statement, his family said:
OL,7,F"Steven was a much-loved son, brother,
OL,8,Funcle, cousin, and friend, but above
OL,9,Fall else, a devoted husband and loving
OL,10,Ffather. He will be deeply missed by
OL,11,Fhis family and by all who knew and
OL,12,Floved him.
OL,14,F"At this extremely difficult time, the
OL,15,Ffamily are supporting one another,
OL,16,Fwhile being assisted by specially
OL,17,Ftrained officers from Cleveland Police.
OL,19,F"We kindly ask that our privacy is
OL,20,Frespected as we grieve and try to come
OL,21,Fto terms with our loss."
