OL,3,CTributes to 'loving father' allegedly
OL,4,Ckilled in street
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man appeared before
OL,7,FTeesside Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FWednesday 27 May charged with murder
OL,9,Fand attempted grievous bodily harm.
OL,11,FHe was remanded in custody until his
OL,12,Fnext court appearance.
